name: Artoria Pendragon (Swimsuit Ruler) (Fate) LoRA
description:
!!! You need this extension in order to use this. Please follow the instructions on the github page to use.
https://github.com/kohya-ss/sd-webui-additional-networks

This is a LoRA for Artoria Pendragon (Swimsuit Ruler) from Fate series.

Use the Strict version if you want to create the white swimsuit outfit. Custom outfits work on both but it is easier with the Flexible version (if it is still not enough, consider lowering the strength of the LoRA).

More details:

https://huggingface.co/breakcore2/loras

Example images with prompts:

https://gist.github.com/breakcore2/236369a988c9638c9500b322eb1adcc9

When prompting for her original outfit:

artoria pendragon \(swimsuit ruler\) \(fate\), ahoge, blonde hair, green eyes, french braid, pony tail, bare shoulders, large breasts, cleavage, clothing cut out, wrist cuffs, detached collar, navel cutout, white leotard, blue necktie, blue pantyhose

Additional costume elements:

thigh strap, pouch

feather boa (the white scarf behind her)

rabbit ears, fake animal ears

When prompting for custom outfit:

artoria pendragon, ahoge, blonde hair, green eyes, french braid, pony tail

To increase modesty:

Add this to negative prompt: nsfw, skirt lift, covered navel, cleavage
